y%20associated%20with%20Jagtar%20Singh%20Tara%2C%20Khalistan%20Tiger%20Force%20(KTF)%20Chief%2C%20it%20added.%20After%20his%20name%20cropped%20up%20in%20several%20terrorism%20cases%2C%20Nijjar%20escaped%20to%20Canada%20in%201996.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20allegedly%20came%20in%20touch%20with%20Pakistan%20based%20KTF%20Chief%2C%20Jagtar%20Singh%20Tara.%20He%20also%20visited%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20garb%20of%20a%20Baisakhi%20jatha%20member%20in%20April%202012%20and%20underwent%20an%20arms%20and%20explosive%20training%20there%20for%20a%20fortnight%2C%20the%20dossier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20returning%20to%20Canada%2C%20he%20allegedly%20started%20arranging%20funds%20for%20terror%20activities%20through%20his%20associates%20engaged%20in%20drugs%20and%20arms%20smuggling%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20planned%20with%20Jagtar%20Singh%20Tara%20to%20execute%20a%20terror%20attack%20in%20Punjab%20and%20raised%20a%20gang%20in%20Canada%20which%20included%20Mandeep%20Singh%20Dhaliwal%2C%20Sarbjit%20Singh%2C%20Anupveer%20Singh%2C%20and%20Darshan%20Singh%20alias%20Fauji%2C%20the%20dossier%20claims%2C%20adidng%20that%20they%20received%20arms%20training%20in%20British%20Columbia%2C%20Canada%20in%20December%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Nijjar%20allegedly%20planned%20to%20execute%20a%20terror%20attack%20on%20Dera%20Sacha%20Sauda%20Headquarters%20in%20Haryana's%20Sirsa%2C%20but%20he%20couldn't%20reach%20India%2C%20the%20dossier%20said%2C%20so%20he%20directed%20his%20module%20to%20target%20former%20DGP%20Mohd%20Izhar%20Alam%2C%20Punjab%20based%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader%20Nishant%20Sharma%2C%20and%20Baba%20Mann%20Singh%20Pehowa%20Wale.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20also%20worked%20with%20Punjab-based%20gangster%20Arshdeep%20Singh%20Gill%20alias%20Arsh%20Dala%20from%20Moga%20to%20carry%20out%20terror%20activities%20in%20Punjab%2C%20the%20dossier%20said.%20He%20allegedly%20tasked%20Arshdeep%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20double-murder%20of%20Manohar%20Lal%20Arora%20and%20Jatinderbir%20Singh%20Arora%2C%20the%20father-son%20duo%20accused%20of%20'anti-Panthic%20activities'%2C%20in%202020.%20In%20the%20attack%2C%20Manohar%20Lal%20was%20shot%20dead%20at%20his%20residence%20in%20Bathinda%20on%20November%2020%2C%202020%2C%20but%20his%20son%20escaped.%20Nijjar%20had%20sent%20money%20from%20Canada%20for%20their%20murder%2C%20the%20dossier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Nijjar%20allegedly%20asked%20Arshdeep%20to%20murder%20the%20priest%20of%20Bhar%20Singh%20Pura%20village%20(Nijjar's%20native%20place).%20However%2C%20the%20priest%20survived.%20Nijjar%2C%20in%20this%20manner%2C%20allegedly%20built%20an%20ecosystem%20of%20terror%20in%20Punjab%20from%20behind%20the%20scenes%20in%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENijjar%20was%20gunned%20down%20outside%20a%20Gurdwara%20in%20a%20parking%20area%20in%20Canada's%20Surrey%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20on%20June%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20today%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkhalistani-terrorist-hardeep-singh-nijjar-killing-canada-pm-justin-trudeaus-fresh-charge-deepens-diplomatic-row-with-india-4415993%5C%22%3Edoubled%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20his%20explosive%20charge%20that%20%26quot%3BIndian%20government%20agents%26quot%3B%20were%20behind%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar's%20killing%2C%20claiming%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20allegations%26quot%3B%20were%20shared%20with%20India%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrudeau%20had%20first%20linked%20Nijjar's%20killing%20to%20India%20on%20Monday%2C%20prompting%20a%20quick%20and%20stern%20denial%20by%20India.%20Canada%20has%20shared%20no%20specific%20information%20regarding%20its%20charges%2C%20India%20said%2C%20flagging%20%26quot%3Bpolitically%20condoned%20hate%20crimes%20and%20criminal%20violence%26quot%3B%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20allegation%20triggered%20tit-for-tat%20moves%20like%20expelling%20diplomats%20that%20escalated%20underlying%20tensions%20t