%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103885873.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVeteran%20Bollywood%20actress%20Zeenat%20Aman%2C%20who%20recently%20joined%20Instagram%2C%20shared%20pictures%20from%20a%20set%20and%20revealed%20that%20she%20has%20been%20unwell%20for%20the%20past%20ten%20days.%20In%20the%20post%2C%20she%20mentioned%20her%20work%20schedule%20and%20how%20her%20glam%20team%20transforms%20her%20look.%20She%20also%20expressed%20her%20joy%20of%20working%20with%20female%20directors%20and%20DOPs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fzeenat-aman-reveals-she-has-been-bedridden-with-horrible-flu-for-past-10-days-shares-update-on-her-health%2Farticleshow%2F103885873.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Himanta%20Sarma's%20Wife%20Files%20Rs%2010%20Crore%20Defamation%20Suit%20Against%20Congress%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERiniki%20Bhuyan%20Sarma%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20Assam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%2C%20has%20filed%20a%20Rs%2010%20crore%20defamation%20suit%20against%20Congress%20MP%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20for%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20allegations%20of%20irregularities%20in%20a%20food%20processing%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Devajit%20Saikia%2C%20her%20counsel%2C%20told%20PTI%20that%20the%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20at%20the%20Court%20of%20Civil%20Judge%20(Senior%20Division)%20of%20Kamrup%20Metropolitan%20on%20Friday%20and%20it%20will%20be%20moved%20on%20September%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20client%20has%20claimed%20a%20defamation%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore%20against%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%20for%20various%20tweets%20on%20X.%20We%20have%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20we%20never%20made%20any%20application%20to%20receive%20subsidy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaikia%20further%20claimed%20that%20the%20process%20to%20seek%20subsidy%20has%20not%20been%20initiated%20at%20all%20and%20for%20which%2C%20a%20show%20cause%20notice%20was%20slapped%20on%20his%20client's%20firm%20on%20May%2026%20this%20year%2C%20followed%20by%20an%20email%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Food%20Processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20approval%20for%20the%20project%20was%20given%20on%20November%2022%2C%202022.%20In%20the%20last%20email%2C%20we%20were%20told%20that%20our%20claim%20would%20lapse%20if%20we%20didn't%20submit%20our%20proposal.%20We%20are%20not%20responding%20to%20anything%20to%20seek%20subsidy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhatever%20Gogoi%20stated%20on%20social%20media%20about%20Sarma%20and%20her%20entity%20'Pride%20East%20Entertainments'%2C%20that%20information%20was%20not%20based%20on%20facts%2C%20claimed%20the%20senior%20advocate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Gogoi)%20did%20not%20do%20his%20homework.%20Getting%20approval%20for%20a%20project%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20a%20subsidy%20has%20been%20received.%20We%20will%20fight%20the%20case%20tooth%20and%20nail%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20huge%20controversy%20erupted%20after%20Guwahati-based%20digital%20media%20'The%20Crosscurrent'%20published%20a%20report%20alleging%20that%20over%2050%20bigha%20(nearly%2017%20acres)%20of%20agricultural%20land%20at%20Darigaji%20village%20in%20Kaliabor%20in%20Nagaon%20district%20was%20reclassified%20as%20industrial%20land%20within%20a%20month%20after%20it%20was%20bought%20by%20Pride%20East%20Entertainments%2C%20in%20which%20the%20chief%20minister's%20wife%20is%20the%20chairman%20and%20managing%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20Gogoi%2C%20in%20a%20series%20of%20tweets%20for%20several%20days%2C%20brought%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20against%20Sarma%20and%20his%20wife%20in%20getting%20central%20government%20subsidy%20for%20the%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Deputy%20Leader%20of%20Congress%20in%20Lok%20Sabha