884962.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Violence-Hit%20Manipur%20To%20Restore%20Mobile%20Internet%20From%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20said%20that%20mobile%20internet%20services%2C%20which%20were%20suspended%20after%20ethnic%20violence%20erupted%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20on%20May%203%2C%20will%20be%20restored%20from%20Saturday.%3Cbr%3E%20He%20also%20called%20for%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20free%20movement%20regime%20that%20allows%20people%20residing%20close%20to%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border%20to%20venture%2016%20km%20deep%20into%20each%20other's%20territory%20without%20any%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20here%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20had%20suspended%20mobile%20internet%20services%20on%20May%203%20to%20check%20the%20spread%20of%20fake%20news%2C%20propaganda%20and%20hate%20speech.%20However%2C%20with%20the%20improvement%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20mobile%20internet%20services%20will%20be%20restored%20across%20the%20state%20from%20today.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20government%20will%20continue%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20influx%20of%20%26quot%3Billegal%20immigrants%26quot%3B%20and%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20complete%20fencing%20of%20the%20India-Myanmar%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20has%20taken%20steps%20to%20fence%2060%20km%20of%20the%20international%20border%20in%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20claimed%20that%20the%20present%20situation%20was%20a%20result%20of%20unplanned%20policies%20of%20the%20previous%20governments%2C%20and%20not%20an%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20any%20recent%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government%20has%20requested%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20to%20cancel%20the%20free%20movement%20regime.%20Also%2C%20security%20forces%20have%20not%20properly%20guarded%20the%20border.%20Instead%20of%20being%20deployed%20at%20zero%20point%2C%20they%20were%20found%20guarding%20the%20border%2014-15%20km%20inside%20Indian%20territory%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20came%20out%20strongly%20against%20the%20bandh%20culture%20and%20incidents%20of%20%26quot%3Brampant%20verbal%20abuse%20against%20MLAs%2C%20ministers%20and%20police%20officials%2C%20which%20has%20diverted%20people%20from%20real%20issues%20and%20created%20conflict%20among%20ourselves%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20last%20two%20months%2C%20the%20situation%20has%20improved%20and%20the%20frequency%20of%20firing%20incidents%20has%20come%20down%20with%20the%20deployment%20of%20security%20forces%20in%20vulnerable%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20claimed%20that%20a%20countrywide%20survey%20has%20found%20a%20rise%20in%20drug%20and%20substance%20abuse%20among%20youths%20of%20the%20state%2C%20which%20was%20the%20reason%20why%20his%20government%20launched%20a%20'war%20on%20drugs'%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20continue...%20it%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20more%20strongly%20to%20destroy%20poppy%20plantations%20in%20the%20hills%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiren%20Singh%20said%20that%20incidents%20of%20extortion%2C%20kidnappings%2C%20and%20perpetrating%20other%20crimes%20by%20miscreants%20impersonating%20policemen%20have%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20stay%20focused%20on%20real%20issues%20in%20the%20state%2C%20namely%20dealing%20with%20influx%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%2C%20taking%20up%20welfare%20activities%20for%20internally%20displaced%20people%2C%20and%20fighting%20massive%20poppy%20cultivation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20objective%20of%20establishing%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20in%20Churachandpur%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Moreh%2C%20and%20Imphal%2C%20our%20government%20is%20taking%20up%20multiple%20initiatives%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20175%20people%20have%20been%20killed%2C%20and%20several%20hundreds%20injured%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Manipur%20on%20May%203%2C%20when%20a%20'Tribal%20Solidarity%20March'%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community's%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeiteis%20account%20for%20about%2053%20per%20cent%20of%20Manipur's%20population%20and%20live%20mostly%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20while%20tribals%2C%20including%20Nagas%20and%20Kukis%2C%20constitute%2040%20per%20cent%20and%20reside%20mostly%20in%20the%20hill%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695454020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqo85i0so_biren-singh-ani_650x400_21_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-mobile-internet-restored-today-mobile-internet-services-to-be-restored-in-manipur-from-saturday-4416357%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20said%20that%20mobile%20internet%20services%2C%20which%20were%20suspended%20after%20ethnic%20violence%20erupted%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%20on%20May%203%2C%20will%20be%20restored%20from%20Saturday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-mobile-internet-restored-today-mobile-internet-services-to-be-restored-in-manipur-from-saturday-4416357%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-mobile-internet-restored-today-mobile-internet-services-to-be-restored-in-manipur-from-saturday-4416357%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.