res-what-we-know-%2Farticleshow%2F103884316.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Waist-Deep%20Water%20Inside%20Nagpur%20Homes%20As%20Heavy%20Rain%20Batters%20City%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHeavy%20rains%20flooded%20many%20parts%20of%20Nagpur%20city%2C%20following%20which%20180%20people%2C%20including%2040%20students%20from%20a%20school%20for%20the%20hearing%20and%20speech-impaired%2C%20were%20rescued%2C%20said%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavi%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Disaster%20Response%20(NDRF)%20and%20State%20Disaster%20Response%20Force%20(SDRF)%20are%20rescuing%20people%20from%20flooded%20homes%20and%20streets.%20Two%20Army%20units%20are%20reaching%20the%20Ambazari%20area%2C%20where%20a%20lake%20overflowed%2C%20said%20Fadnavis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20city%20received%20torrential%20downpours%20from%20Friday%20midnight.%20According%20to%20the%20weather%20department%2C%20Nagpur%20airport%20reported%20106%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20till%205.30%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESeveral%20roads%20and%20residential%20areas%20have%20been%20inundated%20due%20to%20heavy%20rains%2C%20said%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20declared%20a%20holiday%20for%20schools%20and%20colleges%20as%20a%20precautionary%20measure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFadnavis%2C%20who%20is%20an%20MLA%20from%20Nagpur%2C%20took%20to%20X%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20share%20that%20he%20was%20continuously%20monitoring%20the%20rain%20situation%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20incessant%20rainfall%20due%20to%20which%20the%20Ambazari%20lake%20is%20overflowing.%20The%20low-lying%20area%20around%20it%20is%20affected%20more%20due%20to%20this.%20Other%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20too%20are%20affected%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20his%20office%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20deputy%20CM%20has%20instructed%20the%20Nagpur%20collector%2C%20municipal%20commissioner%20and%20police%20commissioner%20to%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%20activate%20multiple%20teams%20for%20rescuing%20people%20who%20are%20stuck%20at%20few%20places%E2%80%9D%2C%20Fadnavis's%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Fadnavis%20said%20on%20X%20that%20two%20units%20of%20NDRF%20and%20two%20units%20of%20SDRF%2C%20which%20were%20divided%20into%207%20groups%2C%20had%20rescued%20140%20citizens.%20Similarly%2C%2040%20students%20were%20rescued%20from%20a%20school%20for%20the%20hearing%20and%20speech-impaired%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20fire%20department%20is%20also%20carrying%20out%20rescue%20work%2C%20the%20deputy%20CM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFadnavis%20also%20appealed%20to%20people%20not%20to%20believe%20in%20any%20rumours.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Nagpur%20Municipal%20Corporation%20has%20advised%20people%20not%20to%20step%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20unless%20necessary.%20Due%20to%20continuous%20rains%2C%20many%20city%20roads%20are%20waterlogged%2C%20it%20said%20waterlogged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Nagpur%20centre%20of%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20said%20%E2%80%9Csevere%2Fmoderate%20thunderstorm%20with%20lightning%E2%80%9D%20will%20likely%20continue%20at%20isolated%20places%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20Bhandara%20and%20Gondia%20districts.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20possibility%20of%20%E2%80%9Cintense%20rain%20at%20isolated%20places%E2%80%9D%20in%20these%20areas%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELight%20to%20moderate%20rainfall%20is%20likely%20to%20occur%20at%20many%20places%20in%20Wardha%20and%20some%20parts%20of%20Chandrapur%2C%20Bhandara%20and%20Gondia%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELight%20rainfall%20is%20very%20likely%20to%20occur%20at%20isolated%20places%20over%20Amravati%2C%20Yavatmal%20and%20Gadchiroli%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3