inion%3A%20JDS-BJP%20Pact%20Could%20Be%20First%20Step%20Towards%20Ending%20Karnataka's%20%26quot%3BAdjustment%20Politics%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EElectoral%20necessities%20almost%20always%20outweigh%20ideological%20foundations%20while%20forging%20political%20alliances.%20Hence%2C%20it's%20no%20surprise%20for%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20H.D.%20Deve%20Gowda's%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%2C%20which%20as%20the%20name%20suggests%20has%20little%20ideological%20affinity%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20to%20join%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20JDS%20and%20BJP%20have%20been%20allies%20in%20the%20past%20-%20the%20BS%20Yediyurappa-led%20BJP%20state%20unit%20formed%20a%20coalition%20government%20in%20Karnataka%20with%20Deve%20Gowda's%20son%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20in%202006%20-%20the%20entry%20of%20the%20JDS%20into%20the%20NDA%20now%20is%20a%20very%20different%20chapter%20in%20the%20regional%20party's%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fen6p203c_bjp-jds-1200_625x300_22_September_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20JDS%20will%20form%20a%20pre-poll%20alliance%20while%20it%20is%20not%20in%20power%20running%20a%20coalition%20government%20in%20Karnataka.%20It%20has%20always%20wielded%20the%20%26quot%3Bbrute%26quot%3B%20post-poll%20bargaining%20power.%20Whenever%20Kumaraswamy%20had%20forged%20an%20alliance%2C%20it%20was%20to%20occupy%20the%20Chief%20Minster's%20post.%20In%202019%2C%20he%20fought%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20as%20a%20Congress%20ally%20only%20because%20the%20Congress%20-%20which%20had%2080%20MLAs%20compared%20to%20JDS's%2037%20-%20had%20ceded%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%20to%20him.%20Similarly%2C%20in%202006%20he%20broke%20his%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20had%20to%20give%20up%20Chief%20Ministership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20JDS%20is%20at%20its%20lowest%20ebb.%20It%20was%20battered%20by%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%2C%20ending%20up%20with%20just%2019%20seats%20and%20a%2013%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%2C%20its%20lowest%20ever%20since%20its%20formation%20in%201999.%20So%2C%20this%20time%20it's%20an%20alliance%20for%20the%20very%20survival%20for%20the%20regional%20force.%20The%20BJP%20is%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%20and%20in%20it%20for%20the%20long%20run.%20There%20are%20compelling%20regional%20reasons%20for%20the%20national%20party%20too%20for%20entering%20this%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20known%20fact%20that%2C%20traditionally%2C%20the%20BJP's%20Achilles%20heel%20in%20Karnataka%20has%20been%20JDS%20strongholds%20and%20the%20regional%20party's%20core%20OBC%20Vokkaliga%20caste%20vote%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%2025%20of%20the%2028%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%202019%20and%20lost%20the%20seats%20of%20Bengaluru%20Rural%20(won%20by%20the%20Congress's%20DK%20Suresh)%2C%20Mandya%20(won%20by%20Congress%20rebel%20and%20independent%20candidate%20Sumalatha)%20and%20Hassan%20(won%20by%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda's%20grandson%20Prajwal%20Revanna).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20for%20the%20Hassan%20parliamentary%20seat%20was%20A%20Manju%2C%20who%20was%20a%20JDS%20rebel%20and%20later%20returned%20to%20the%20party%20and%20won%20the%20Hassan%20assembly%20seat%20in%202023.%20The%20BJP%20has%20never%20won%20these%20three%20seats%2C%20despite%20winning%20at%20least%2017%20of%20the%2028%20parliamentary%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20consistently%20since%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20seats%2C%20along%20with%20five%20more%2C%20define%20the%20JDS%20region%20of%20electoral%20influence.%20In%20an%20assembly%20poll%20this%20translates%20to%20around%2050%20seats.%20From%20the%20BJP's%20point%20of%20view%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20JDS%20is%20the%20first%20step%20to%20a%20decisive%20reworking%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20political%20arithmetic%2C%20both%20for%20the%20parliamentary%20polls%20of%202024%20and%20beyond.%20It%20needs%20to%20take%20over%20the%20JDS%20vote%20base%2C%20a%20strongly%20caste-affiliated%20voter%20who%20is%20essentially%20anti-Congress%20at%20the%20grassroots.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20already%20considered%20the%20bastion%20of%20Karnataka's%20largest%20voting%20bloc%20-%20the%20Lingayat%20sect.%20The%20OBC%20Vokkaliga%20caste%20base%20of%20the%20JDS%20is%20the%20second%20largest%20vote%20bloc%20of%20Karnataka.%20While%20the%20Lingayats%20are%20spread%20across%20Karnataka%20the%20Vokkaligas%20are%20concentrated%20in%20the%20JDS's%20region%20of%20influence.%20Uniting%20the%20two%20is%20a%20recipe%20for%20success%2C%20but%20it%20is%20easier%20said%20than%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20seems%20to%20be%20looking%20at%20the%20JDS%20eventually%20merging%20with%20it%2C%20like%20many%20small%20splinters%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20Janata%20movement%20have%20in%20other%20states%2C%20and%20that%20would%20create%20a%20bipolar%20Congress%20versus%20BJP%20narrative%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20the%20BJP%20has%20never%20won%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20the%20southern%20state%2C%20despite%20having%20swept%20parliamentary%20polls%2C%20is%20because%20of%20its%20weakness%20in%20the%20JDS%20heartland.%20In%20an%20assembly%20poll%20a%20three-way%20fight%20has%20always%20benefited%20the%20Congress%20on%20JDS%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20in%202023%2C%20the%20BJP%20went%20after%20the%20JDS%20vote%20in%20Old%20Mysore%20and%20that%20helped%20the%20Congress%20sweep%20the%20region.%20OBC%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20State%20Congress%20President%20DK%20Shivakumar%20is%20from%20the%20Vokkaliga%20caste%20and%20dedicated%20himself%20hugely%20towards%20decimating%20the%20JDS%20in%20districts%20like%20Mandya.%20His%20job%20was%20made%20easier%20by%20the%20BJP%20splitting%20the%20JDS%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBeyond%20this%20straightforward%20calculation%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20strong%20third%20player%20in%20the%20JDS%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20Karnataka's%20notorious%20%26quot%3Badjustment%20politics%26quot%3B.%20Under-the-table%20political%20arrangements%2C%20family%20ties%20and%20business%20relationships%20between%20powerful%20political%20families%20in%20several%20constituencies%20go%20beyond%20party%20lines.%20While%20such%20dealings%20are%20a%20reality%20of%20Indian%20politics%2C%20it%20may%20be%20argued%20that%20they%20are%20far%20more%20prevalent%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt's%20possibly%20why%20Karnataka%20has%20the%20richest%20MLAs%20in%20the%20country%20and%20despite%20the%20state%20never%20voting%20an%20incumbent%20government%20to%20power%20since%201985%2C%20there%20are%20incumbent%20candidates%20who%20have%20never%20lost%20their%20seats%20for%20decades.%20They%20shift%20parties%20with%20impunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDominant%20sections%20of%20the%20BJP's%20central%20leadership%20have%20held%20this%20as%20a%20main%20reason%20for%20the%20party's%20inability%20to%20win%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20the%20state%20despite%20sweeping%20parliamentary%20polls.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%202023%2C%20the%20BJP%20made%20an%20effort%20to%20work%20around%20these%20arrangements%2C%20but%20failed%20miserably.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20%26quot%3Badjustment%20politics%26quot%3B%20is%20also%20the%20reason%20the%20Congress's%20central%20leadership%20is%20careful%20in%20Karnataka%20decisions.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%202019%2C%20when%20the%20Congress-JDS%20alliance%20was%20toppled%20in%20the%20state%2C%20many%2C%20if%20not%20most%2C%20of%20the%2013%20Congress%20MLAs%20who%20resigned%20and%20switched%20to%20the%20BJP%20to%20support%20BS%20Yediyurappa%20were%20considered%20loyalists%20of%20present%20Chief%20Minister%20Siddaramiah%2C%20who%20himself%20shifted%20to%20the%20Congress%20from%20the%20JDS%20in%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20MLAs%20are%20now%20looking%20at%20a%20return%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20have%20publicly%20displayed%20their%20proximity%20to%20Yediyurappa%2C%20who%20was%20a%20master%20at%20striking%20alliances%20with%20MLAs%20cutting%20across%20party%20lines%20to%20get%20the%20BJP%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20central%20leadership%20has%20been%20keen%20to%20end%20this%20%26quot%3Badjustment%20politics%26quot%3B%20because%20it%20limits%20the%20party's%20hold%20on%20the%20government%20and%20also%20confines%20its%20growth%20in%20the%20state.%20Sections%20of%20the%20state%20leadership%20haven't%20yielded%20yet.%20Having%20a%20strong%20third%20player%20in%20the%20JDS%20is%20the%20first%20hurdle%20in%20ending%20such%20adjustments.%20So%2C%20the%20national%20party%20will%20use%20every%20weapon%20in%20its%20arsenal%20to%20ensure%20the%20JDS%20vote%20transfers%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%202024%20and%20the%20seat%20sharing%20arrangement%20is%20likely%20to%20reflect%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20if%20the%202024%20experiment%20works%20out%20for%20the%20BJP%20-%20nationally%20and%20locally%20-%20it%20will%20forge%20ahead%20in%20cannibalizing%20the%20JDS%20vote.%20The%20JDS%20is%20in%20no%20position%20to%20fight%20back.%20There%20are%20multiple%20factions%20in%20the%20Deve%20Gowda%20family.%20HD%20Kumaraswamy's%20brother%20and%20former%20minister%20HD%20Revanna%20is%20considered%20closer%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20JDS%20disintegrates%20after%202024%2C%20different%20factions%20may%20head%20different%20ways%20and%2C%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one%2C%20Kumaraswamy's%20entry%20into%20the%20NDA%20may%20well%20be%20the%20start%20of%20a%20long%20road%20with%20the%20BJP.%20A%20road%20where%20the%20BJP%20runs%20the%20show%20for%20him%20and%20one%20that%20could%20redefine%20Karnataka's%20political%20arithmetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20Deve%20Gowda%2C%20who%20had%20claimed%20to%20be%20the%20secular%20ally%20of%20the%20Left%20Democratic%20Front%20in%20Kerala%20for%20years%2C%20may%20serve%20more%20proof%20that%20ideological%20positions%20are%20conveniently%20forgotten%20when%20his%20party%20tries%20to%20%26quot%3Brise%20from%20the%20ashes%20like%20a%20phoenix%26quot%3B!%20(Gowda%20had%20famously%20told%20reporters%20he%20would%20rise%20like%20a%20phoenix%20when%20he%20was%20unseated%20as%20Prime%20Minster%20in%201997)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(TM%20Veeraraghav%20is%20the%20Executive%20Editor%2C%20BQ%20Prime.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695448140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fen6p203c_bjp-jds-1200_625x300_22_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fjds-bjp-pact-could-be-first-step-towards-ending-karnatakas-adjustment-politics-4416275%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20JDS%20and%20BJP%20have%20been%20allies%20in%20the%20past%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20the%20JDS%20into%20the%20NDA%20now%20is%20a%20very%20different%20chapter%20in%20the%20regional%20party's%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fjds-bjp-pact-could-be-first-step-towards-ending-karnatakas-adjustment-politics-4416275%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Srishti%3A%20Vicky%20is%20the%20most%20loved%20person%20on%20the%20set%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695447930000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103882703%2Cimgsize-97132.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsrishti-dixit-vic