ess%20that%20can%20take%20several%20years%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20data%20from%20Chandrayaan-1%20is%20still%20producing%20publications.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20freewheeling%20conversation%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Somanath%20discussed%20challenges%20with%20the%20earlier%20moon%20mission%2C%20described%20in%20detail%20the%20workings%20of%20the%20lander%20and%20the%20rover%2C%20and%20his%20vision%20for%20the%20future%20of%20space%20research%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission%20%26quot%3Ba%20very%20hard%20learning%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20organisation%2C%20and%20said%20they%20conducted%20rigorous%20review%20to%20understand%20what%20could%20have%20gone%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20not%20possible%20to%20recover%20the%20debris%20and%20then%20study%20it%2C%20so%20it%20has%20to%20be%20now%20simulated%20and%20synthesised%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20look%20at%20the%20possibilities.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20tedious%20journey%20in%20which%20many%20of%20us%2C%20with%20various%20skill%20sets%2C%20participated%2C%20and%20that%20contributed%20to%20the%20understanding%20of%20the%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ISRO%20chief%20said%20it%20was%20very%20clearly%20identified%20that%20it's%20not%20just%20one%20issue%20that%20was%20causing%20the%20problem%2C%20but%20a%20chain%20of%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20primary%20point%20is%20that%20we%20were%20not%20able%20to%20simulate%20everything%20on%20the%20ground%20before%20Chandrayaan-2%2C%20but%20now%20we%20have%20similar%20and%20real%20scenarios%2C%20so%20we%20have%20huge%20amount%20of%20data%20and%20with%20the%20data%20we%20have%20more%20confidence%20to%20modify%20it.%20Once%20you%20look%20at%20modification%2C%20we%20need%20to%20look%20at%20whether%20we%20need%20to%20correct%20only%20those%20issues%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20or%20potential%20issues%20that%20can%20pop%20up%20later%20based%20on%20the%20understanding%2C%20and%20this%20is%20again%20debated%20for%20another%20long%20periods%20of%20time%20what%20should%20be%20done%20in%20extra%20hours%2C%20what%20type%20of%20strengthening%20that%20we%20need%20to%20do%2C%20and%20this%20is%20again%20debated%20over%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time.%20It%20also%20called%20for%20new%20developments%20of%20instruments%2C%20software%20simulations%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20tests%20that%20need%20to%20be%20done%20which%20you%20couldn't%20do%20with%20Chandrayaan-2%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20%26quot%3Bhop%20test%26quot%3B%20successfully%20done%20by%20the%20moon%20lander%2C%20Mr%20Somanath%20explained%20that%20it%20was%20a%20step%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20future%20sample%20return%20and%20human%20missions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20why%20we%20go%20to%20the%20moon%20is%20to%20look%20at%20how%20it%20can%20be%20useful%20to%20humanity.%20For%20that%2C%20we%20need%20to%20go%20to%20the%20moon%20and%20come%20back%2C%20it's%20not%20just%20landing%20there.%20We%20need%20to%20come%20back%20home%20and%20then%20take%20material%20back%20and%20forth.%20So%2C%20we%20looked%20at%20how%20we%20can%20use%20this%20success%20and%20make%20an%20outline%20of%20another%20opportunity%20to%20take%20it%20off%20from%20the%20moon%20and%20go%20to%20orbit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStressing%20on%20the%20need%20for%20such%20missions%2C%20he%20said%20if%20humanity%20is%20going%20to%20travel%20beyond%20earth%2C%20habitat%20creation%20is%20needed%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20Mars%2C%20and%20exoplanets%2C%20and%20Indians%20must%20be%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20think%20of%20ourselves%20as%20so%20inferior%20today%2C%20that%20we%20are%20not%20technologically%20advanced%2C%20not%20financially%20very%20powerful%2C%20and%20we%20always%20think%20that%20we%20are%20poor%2C%20so%20we%20can't%20invest%20in%20all%20of%20this.%20I%20believe%20that%20this%20has%20to%20go%2C%20for%20a%20nation%20which%20thinks%20that%20they%20are%20the%20one%20who%20are%20creators%20of%20knowledge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20countries%20like%20US%20and%20the%20USSR%20became%20big%20only%20because%20they%20started%20dreaming%20about%20becoming%20a%20world%20power%2C%20Mr%20Somanath%20said%2C%20but%20clarified%20the%20type%20of%20world%20power%20he%20wants%20India%20to%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20question%20of%20the%20world%20power%20is%20very%2C%20very%20important.%20Not%20the%20power%20that%20we%20always%20talk%20about%2C%20like%20the%20military%20power%2C%20the%20strength%20to%20capture%20others.%20I%20believe%20India%20should%20become%20a%20technology%20leader%20in%20the%20future%2C%20because%20when%20you%20are%20a%20technology%20leader%20you%20are%20naturally%20somebody%20who%20has%20no%20second%20thought%20about%20possibilities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ISRO%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ES%20Somanath%20also%20batted%20for%20private%20investment%20in%20space%20research%2C%20arguing%20that%20we%20can't%20be%20a%20technologically%20powerful%20nation%20without%20being%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20some%20of%20the%20knowledge%20in%20the%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20can%20happen%2C%20not%20from%20government%2C%20only%20from%20private%20entrepreneurs%20where%20they%20sponsor%20research.%20I%20am%20a%20very%20strong%20believer%20on%20this%2C%20that%20unless%20big%20players%20in%20the%20industry%20invest%20in%20research%20and%20development%2C%20and%20bank%20on%20for%20their%20commercial%20outcome%2C%20nothing%20can%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695446220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fsi9cgr68_isro-chief-_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-updates-isro-satisfied-with-data-isro-chief-s-somanath-discusses-chandrayaan-3-challenges-4416190%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20freewheeling%20conversation%20wi