22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-nishikant-dubey-questions-danish-alis-conduct-day-after-he-was-abused-by-ramesh-bidhuri-4416175%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-nishikant-dubey-questions-danish-alis-conduct-day-after-he-was-abused-by-ramesh-bidhuri-4416175%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjps-nishikant-dubey-questions-danish-alis-conduct-day-after-he-was-abused-by-ramesh-bidhuri-4416175%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'What%20You%20Are%20Trying%20Is%20Beyond%20My%20Comprehension'%3A%20Shami%20Stumps%20Reporter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENot%20used%20to%20being%20benched%20by%20the%20Indian%20team%20management%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%20has%20seen%20his%20game-time%20being%20limited%20in%20the%2050-over%20format%20over%20the%20last%20few%20matches.%20But%2C%20as%20Shami%20featured%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%20against%20Australia%20for%20the%20first%20ODI%2C%20the%20veteran%20pacer%20bagged%205%20wickets%2C%20giving%20a%20fine%20example%20of%20the%20talent%20and%20skills%20he%20brings%20to%20the%20table.%20While%20sitting%20on%20the%20bench%20isn't%20something%20any%20player%20enjoys%2C%20Shami%20said%20that%20even%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%2C%20there%20were%20some%20players%20who%20missed%20out.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20playing%20regularly%2C%20there%20must%20have%20been%20someone%2C%20who%20had%20to%20sit%20out%20and%20I%20wasn't%20guilty.%20So%20you%20can't%20feel%20low%20if%20you%20are%20sitting%20out%20because%20the%20team%20is%20winning%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20pragmatic%20Mohammed%20Shami%20told%20reporters%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20after%20India's%20victory%20over%20Australia%20in%20the%20first%20ODI%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20management%20has%20indicated%20that%20when%20it%20plays%20full%20strength%20during%20the%20upcoming%20World%20Cup%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20and%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20will%20be%20the%20two%20front-line%20pacers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20his%20match-winning%20figures%20of%205%20for%2051%2C%20Shami%20said%20that%20rotation%20isn't%20a%20bad%20thing%20when%20you%20play%20so%20many%20matches%20on%20the%20bounce.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20team's%20plan%20and%20it%20is%20important%20to%20stick%20with%20it.%20You%20can't%20be%20always%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%20because%20a%20lot%20depends%20on%20the%20team%20combination%2C%26quot%3B%20Shami%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20playing%2C%20well%20and%20good%20and%20if%20you%20are%20not%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%2C%20then%20you%20should%20be%20supportive%20of%20those%2C%20who%20are%20playing.%20I%20think%20there%20is%20no%20point%20feeling%20low%20and%20I%20am%20ready%20to%20play%20the%20role%20the%20team%20gives%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Shami%20said%20as%20he%20steered%20clear%20of%20anything%20that%20could%20be%20remotely%20controversial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20asked%20if%20he%20approves%20of%20this%20rotation%20policy%20where%20he%20has%20to%20sit%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20you%20are%20trying%20to%20know%20is%20beyond%20my%20comprehension%20but%20obviously%20when%20you%20build%20a%20team%2C%20(the)%20coach%20has%20a%20role%20to%20rotate%20players%20and%2C%20based%20on%20the%20situation%2C%20it%20is%20decided%2C%26quot%3B%20Shami%20said%20with%20a%20wry%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20rotation%20before%20a%20big%20event%20like%20the%20World%20Cup%20is%20a%20good%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20seen%20we%20have%20(had)%20got%20results%20due%20to%20rotation%20and%20I%20believe%20before%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20put%20too%20much%20workload%20in%20back-to-back%20games%2C%20and%20its%20going%20well%20and%20we%20are%20getting%20good%20results.%26quot%3B%20Shami%20had%20taken%20a%20break%20after%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20and%20he%20didn't%20travel%20to%20the%20West%20Indies%20for%20the%20two%20Tests%20and%20three%20ODIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20important%20to%20take%20that%20break%20because%20I%20had%20played%20back-to-back%20games%20continuously%20for%207-8%20months.%20At%20the%20back%20of%20my%20head%2C%20I%20felt%20I%20needed%20a%20break%20for%20a%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20discussed%20with%20coach%20(Rahul%20Dravid)%20and%20captain%20(Rohit%20Sharma)%20and%20took%20a%20break%20(from%20the%20West%20Indies%20series).%20But%20my%20break%20never%20seemed%20like%20a%20break%20for%20me%20because%20I%20have%20an%20elaborate%20training%20set-up%20at%20home%20(Sahaspur%20in%20UP's%20Amroha)%20and%20I%20end%20up%20training%20more%20at%20home%20than%20when%20I%20am%20with%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20asked%20if%20he%20did%20anything%20special%20to%20dismiss%20Steve%20Smith%2C%20but%20his%20answer%20was%20in%20the%20negative.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20tried%20to%20do%20my%20basics%20right%20and%20hit%20the%20top%20of%20off-stump%20and%20wait%20for%20the%20batters%20to%20make%20a%20mistake.%26quot%3B%20The%20conditions%20were%20humid%20and%20Shami%20was%20used%20in%20small%20spells.%20Could%20it%20be%20a%20template%20going%20into%20the%20World%20Cup%3F%20%26quot%3BIt%20depends%20on%20the%20situation.%20How%20a%20partnership%20(is)%20going%20and%20how%20well%20you%20are%20bowling%20at%20that%20time.%20Sometimes%2C%20you%20end%20up%20bowling%20a%20six-over%20spell%20as%20well%20while%20sometimes%20you%20bowl%20only%20three%20overs.%26quot%3B%20He%20admitted%20that%20heat%20does%20a%20play%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20heat%20does%20play%20a%20part%20and%20we%20are%20also%20human%20beings.%20It%20takes%20a%20toll%20on%20our%20bodies%20and%20on%20stamina.%20But%20when%20you%20have%20played%20international%20cricket%20for%20so%2