ation%E2%80%9D%20with%20India%20%E2%80%9Cmany%20weeks%20ago%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Friday%2C%20Blinken%20said%20that%20the%20United%20States%20was%20%E2%80%9Cdeeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20allegations%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Trudeau%20has%20raised%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20US%20national%20security%20advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20observed%20that%20no%20country%20could%20get%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fnijjar-killing-us-canada-no-special-exemption%5C%22%3Especial%20exemption%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20for%20such%20activities%20like%20the%20allegations%20made%20by%20Canada%20of%20involvement%20of%20Indian%20government%20agents%20in%20Nijjar%E2%80%99s%20killing.%20Sullivan%20had%20also%20urged%20India%20to%20join%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20been%20consulting%20throughout%20very%20closely%20with%20our%20Canadian%20colleague%2C%20not%20just%20consulting%2C%20coordinating%20on%20this%20issue.%20And%20from%20our%20perspective%2C%20it%20is%20critical%20that%20the%20Canadian%20investigation%20proceeds%20and%20it%20would%20be%20important%20that%20India%20work%20with%20the%20Canadians%20on%20this%20investigation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Blinken%20said%20on%20Friday%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20US%20wanted%20to%20see%20%E2%80%9Caccountability%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-canada-nijjar-modi%5C%22%3ECanada%E2%80%99s%20Allegation%20Creates%20a%20Dissonance%20in%20the%20Post-G20%20Narratives%20About%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20had%20raised%20the%20issue%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20speak%20about%20diplomatic%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEchoing%20Sullivan%E2%80%99s%20words%20about%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20case%2C%20Blinken%20said%20that%20the%20US%20was%20%E2%80%9Cextremely%20vigilant%20against%20any%20instances%20of%20transnational%20repression%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20it%E2%80%99s%20important%2C%20more%20broadly%2C%20for%20the%20international%20system%20that%20any%20country%20that%20might%20consider%20engaging%20in%20such%20acts%20not%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20made%20an%20unprecedented%20explosive%20statement%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20House%20of%20Commons%20that%20Canada%20was%20pursuing%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20allegations%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpotential%20link%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20killing%20of%20Nijjar%20and%20%E2%80%9Cagents%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%20India%20described%20the%20allegations%20as%20%E2%80%9Cabsurd%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmotivated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Canada%20expelled%20a%20senior%20Indian%20diplomat%2C%20India%20did%20the%20same%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20further%20escalated%20its%20response%20stopping%20all%20visa%20operations%20for%20Canadian%20nationals.%20The%20Canadian%20High%20Commission%20also%20began%20downsizing%20its%20presence%20in%20India%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20number%20of%20diplomats.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20making%20any%20commitment%20to%20join%20the%20investigation%2C%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20had%20said%20that%20India%20was%20%E2%80%9Cwilling%20to%20look%E2%80%9D%20at%20any%20specific%20information%2C%20but%20Canada%20had%20not%20shared%20any%20such%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Trudea%20contradicted%20India%E2%80%99s%20claims%20that%20Canada%20had%20not%20shared%20any%20%E2%80%9Cspecific%20information%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F