in%20who%20is%20also%20a%20fellow%20at%20the%20American%20Enterprise%20Institute%2C%20where%20he%20specializes%20in%20Iran%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20South%20Asia%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20former%20consumer%20of%20intelligence%2C%20I%20can%20say%20that%20oftentimes%20the%20intelligence%20we%20see%20whether%20it's%20a%20telephone%20intercept%20or%20something%20else%2C%20isn't%20as%20black%20and%20white%2C%20isn't%20as%20cut%20and%20dry.%20I%20mean%2C%20certainly%2C%20that%20was%20the%20case%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20Iraq%20War.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BSo%20when%20you%20have%20a%20situation%20like%20this%2C%20perhaps%20Prime%20Minister%20Trudeau%20raised%20the%20issue%2C%20but%20there%20wasn't%20necessarily%20consensus%20on%20what%20he%20meant.%20And%20regardless%2C%20let's%20not%20fool%20ourselves%2C%20Nijjar%20was%20not%20simply%20a%20plumber%2C%20any%20more%20than%20Osama%20bin%20Laden%20was%20a%20construction%20engineer.%20He%20had%20blood%20on%20his%20hands%20from%20multiple%20attacks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20whether%20the%20US%20will%20publicly%20intervene%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20Mr%20Rubin%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFrankly%2C%20there's%20a%20much%20greater%20danger%20for%20Canada%20than%20India.%20If%20Canada%20wants%20to%20pick%20a%20fight%2C%20frankly%2C%20at%20this%20point%2C%20it's%20like%20an%20ant%20picking%20a%20fight%20against%20an%20elephant%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20matter%20is%20India%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy.%20It's%20far%20more%20important%20strategically%2C%20arguably%20than%20Canada%20is%2C%20especially%20as%20concern%20grows%20with%20regard%20to%20China%20and%20other%20matters%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20basin%2C%20and%20in%20the%20Pacific.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20India-Canada%20ties%20soured%20further%20after%20Canadian%20PM%20Justin%20Trudeau%20alleged%20India's%20role%20behind%20the%20killing%20of%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20both%20countries%20expelling%20a%20senior%20diplomat%20in%20a%20tit-for-tat%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20India%20has%20out-rightly%20denied%20such%20allegations%20calling%20them%20'absurd'%20and%20'motivated'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Canadian%20PM%20has%20failed%20to%20present%20any%20evidence%20to%20back%20his%20claims.%20Trudeau%20was%20repeatedly%20quizzed%20on%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20allegations%20but%20stuck%20to%20reiterating%20that%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bcredible%20reasons%26quot%3B%20to%20believe%20that%20India%20was%20linked%20to%20the%20death%20of%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Pentagon%20official%20further%20slammed%20Trudeau%20and%20said%20that%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20-%20A%20khalistani%20terrorist%20allegedly%20killed%20by%20his%20erstwhile%20comrades%20-%20is%20not%20a%20model%20to%20use%20for%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20rights%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20was%20a%20terrorist%20involved%20in%20multiple%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJustin%20Trudeau%20might%20want%20to%20make%20this%20a%20case%20of%20human%20rights.%20The%20fact%20of%20that%20matter%20is%2C%20that%20Nijjar%20isn't%20a%20model%20one%20wants%20to%20use%20for%20human%20rights.%20Nijjar%20may%20have%20been%20involved%20in%20the%20assassination%20of%20a%20rival%20Sikh%20leader%2C%20just%20a%20year%20ago.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20has%20blood%20on%20his%20hands%20through%20multiple%20attacks.%20He%20entered%20Canada%20with%20a%20fraudulent%20passport.%20And%20the%20fact%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20this%20is%20no%20Mother%20Teresa%2C%20we%20are%20talking%20about.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Rubin%20added%20that%20many%20of%20the%20US%20security%20community%20and%20even%20from%20Canadian%20security%20understand%20that%20Trudeau%20has%20gone%20%26quot%3Btoo%20far%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20Trudeau%20converted%20a%20domestic%20political%20obstacl