pergin%20was%20allegedly%20beaten%2C%20throttled%2C%20scalded%20with%20boiling%20water%2C%20stabbed%2C%20maimed%20and%20violated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20jurors%20were%20told%20that%20the%20couple%20was%20abducted%20when%20they%20were%20returning%20home%20from%20an%20Italian%20restaurant%20in%20Mayfair.%20The%20assailants%20had%20allegedly%20installed%20a%20tracking%20device%20on%20Mr%20Alpergin's%20car%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fcrime%2Flondon-white-hart-lane-essex-mayfair-old-bailey-b2415107.html%5C%22%3Eoutlet%20%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20They%20were%20put%20in%20separate%20vehicles%20and%20taken%20to%20a%20bar%20on%20White%20Hart%20Lane.%20Mr%20Alpergin's%20naked%20body%20was%20later%20dumped%20in%20Essex%20woodland%20and%20his%2034-year-old%20girlfriend%20spent%20two%20days%20locked%20in%20a%20toilet%20before%20being%20freed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESix%20men%20are%20now%20on%20trial%20at%20the%20Central%20Criminal%20Court%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnirav-modi-transferred-to-privately-run-prison-in-london-4411804%5C%22%3ELondon%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20accused%20of%20murder%2C%20kidnap%2C%20false%20imprisonment%20and%20preventing%20the%20course%20of%20justice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20obvious%20that%20before%20his%20death%20Koray%20Alpergin%20had%20been%20stripped%20naked%20and%20horrifically%20tortured.%20From%20the%20number%20and%20nature%20of%20the%20injuries%20sustained%2C%20the%20prosecution%20suggest%20that%20it%20is%20not%20hard%20to%20envisage%20a%20group%20of%20sadistic%20thugs%20taking%20it%20in%20turns%20to%20inflict%20injury%2C%20whether%20with%20punches%20and%20kicks%2C%20hitting%20him%20with%20a%20bat%2C%20scalding%20him%20with%20boiling%20water%2C%20stabbing%20his%20feet...%26quot%3B%20lawyer%20Crispin%20Aylett%20said%2C%20according%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fnews%2F2023%2F09%2F20%2Fmehmet-koray-alpergin-thugs-killed-dj-london-bizim-fm%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Mr%20Aylett%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20attack%20was%20connected%20to%20%26quot%3Borganised%20crime%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Balmost%20certainly%20drugs%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20jurors%20were%20told%20that%20the%2043-year-old%20was%20originally%20from%20northern%20Cyprus.%20He%20was%20a%20well-known%20figure%20in%20the%20British%20Turkish%20community%20and%20owner%20of%20a%20Turkish%20language%20radio%20station%20in%20London%20called%20Bizim%20FM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20the%20jurors%20heard%20that%20before%20his%20death%2C%20Mr%20Alpergin%20was%20not%20his%20usual%20%26quot%3Bhappy-go-lucky%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20seemed%20anxious.%20He%20was%20allegedly%20in%20debt%2C%20including%20around%20%2440%2C000%20for%20his%20car.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Alpergin's%20body%20was%20found%20by%20a%20dog%20walker%20a%20few%20hours%20after%20it%20was%20dumped%20in%20woods%20on%20October%2015%20last%20year.%20Mr%20Aylett%20said%20that%20a%20post-mortem%20report%20identified%2094%20separate%20injuries%20to%20his%20body.%20There%20were%20also%20wounds%20to%20the%20victim's%20genitals%20and%20an%20internal%20injury%2C%20the%20lawyer%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESteffan%20Gordon%2C%2034%2C%20Tejean%20Kennedy%2C%2033%2C%20Samuel%20Owusu-Opoku%2C%2035%2C%20Junior%20Kettle%2C%2032%2C%20Ali%20Kavak%2C%2026%2C%20and%20Erdogan%20Ulcay%2C%2056%2C%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20murder%2C%20kidnapping%2C%20false%20imprisonment%2C%20and%20perverting%20justice.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695442140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fg7ca1n6_dj-mehmet-koray-alpergin_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpopular-dj-in-london-tortured-to-death-by-sadistic-thugs-uk-court-told-4416123%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20pop