%20a%20journalist%20who%20was%20covering%20the%20event%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmid%20massive%20pro-Islam%20and%20pro-Mirwaiz%20slogans%20like%20%E2%80%98Choice%2C%20choice%2C%20Mirwaiz%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20chairman%20made%20his%20way%20towards%20the%20gate%20with%20some%20of%20his%20supporters%2C%20who%20had%20failed%20to%20get%20close%20to%20him%2C%20hurling%20their%20garlands%20on%20him%20before%20he%20entered%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20sermon%2C%20Mirwaiz%20briefly%20touched%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20also%20advocated%20%E2%80%9Cpeaceful%20settlement%20of%20Kashmir%20issue%E2%80%9D%20while%20recalling%20the%20events%20under%20which%20he%20was%20allegedly%20put%20under%20house%20arrest%20by%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20very%20emotional%20moment%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirwaiz%20said%2C%20addressing%20the%20worshippers%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20more%20than%20four%20years.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20be%20away%20from%20you%20for%20such%20a%20long%20time%20has%20been%20very%20difficult%20for%20me.%20But%20you%20my%20people%20are%20my%20strength%20that%20helped%20me%20in%20go%20(sic)%20through%20this%20trying%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Mirwaiz%20said%20that%20India%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20China%20are%20parties%20to%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20has%20to%20be%20addressed%20and%20resolved%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20fact.%20International%20community%20has%20ratified%20this%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20events%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20after%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20have%20left%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20no%20space%20for%20us%20or%20for%20the%20expression%20of%20our%20opinion%20and%20aspirations%20and%20our%20concerns%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20(Kashmir%20issue)%20is%20a%20human%20problem%20for%20us%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%C2%A0%20Kashmir%2C%20not%20a%20territorial%20tug%20of%20war.%C2%A0As%20PM%20(Narendra)%20Modi%20rightly%20said%2C%20this%20is%20not%20an%20era%20of%20war.%20We%20have%20personally%20suffered%20for%20pursuing%20this%20route%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirwaiz%2C%20whose%20father%20was%20assassinated%20on%20May%2021%2C%201990%2C%20said%20in%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20so-called%20separatists%20or%20peace%20disrupters%20but%20realist%20resolution%20seekers.%20We%20have%20always%20believed%20and%20participated%20in%20efforts%20of%20resolution%C2%A0(of%20Kashmir%20issue)%20through%20an%20alternative%20to%20violent%20means%20which%20is%20dialogue%20and%20reconciliation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mirwaiz%2C%20who%20has%20participated%20in%20Indo-Pak%20dialogue%20on%20Kashmir%20under%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%E2%80%99s%20government%2C%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Friday%20prayers%20were%20over%2C%20Mirwaiz%20was%20ushered%20out%20into%20the%20compound%20of%20the%20mosque%20where%20a%20large%20crowd%20of%20his%20supporters%20had%20gathered%20to%20see%20him.%20The%20moderate%20Hurriyat%20chairman%20could%20be%20seen%20greeting%20them%20before%20departing%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695398968000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22212959%2FThe-Wire-16.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjk-sea-of-people-greet-mirwaiz-umar-as-he-delivers-first-sermon-in-four-years-at-jamia-masjid%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20All%20Parties%20Hurriyat%20Conference%20moved%20the%20high%20court%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20lifted%20all%20curbs%20against%20him%20on%20Thursday.%20He%20was%20under%20house%20arrest%20for%20four%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjk-sea-of-people-greet-mi