ns%2C%20CC0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20message%20is%20very%20bad%2C%20both%20for%20Poland%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20but%20also%20because%20Poland%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20chief%20advocates%20of%20military%20aid%20to%20Ukraine.%20Saying%20Poland%20will%20not%20be%20sending%20more%20weapons%20means%20that%20Poland%C2%A0can%20no%20longer%20play%20this%20role%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Baranowski%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20Warsaw-based%20GMF%20East%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20German%20Marshall%20Fund%20think%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20regard%20to%20Poland%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%20saying%20Warsaw%20would%20look%20at%20focusing%20on%20modernising%20its%20own%20forces%2C%20ahead%20of%20assisting%20Kyiv%2C%20Baranowski%20believes%20Poland%20is%20capable%20of%20modernising%20its%20military%20whilst%20continuing%20to%20help%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPoland%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20show%20firmness%20towards%20Kyiv%2C%20Baranowski%20remarked%2C%20should%20be%20understood%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20election%20campaign.%20Any%20solution%2C%20his%20GMF%20colleague%20Jazowska%20added%2C%20can%20only%20be%20found%20after%20Poland%E2%80%99s%20national%20election%20has%20concluded%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPoland%20a%20key%20transit%20country%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20sending%20its%20own%20supplies%20to%20Kyiv%2C%20Poland%20is%20also%20a%20key%20transit%20country%20for%20weaponry%20that%20the%20US%20and%20other%20Western%20countries%20are%20sending%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20Svitlana%20Taran%2C%20a%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20Brussels-based%20European%20Policy%20Centre%20(EPC)%20think%20tank%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EDW%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPoland%20is%20a%20very%20important%20transit%20hub%20for%20Ukraine%20and%20I%20do%20hope%20the%20recent%20remarks%2C%20even%20over%20weapons%2C%20were%20just%20emotional.%20A%20huge%20number%20of%20weapons%20%5Bdestined%20for%5D%20Ukraine%20also%20go%20through%20Poland.%20Meanwhile%2C%20for%20Poland%2C%20Ukraine%20is%20also%20important%20economically%2C%20so%20%5Bthey%5D%20are%20very%20interdependent%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEuropean%20Commission%20spokesperson%20Peter%20Stano%20said%20that%20while%20the%20EU%E2%80%99s%20executive%20branch%20would%20not%20comment%20directly%20on%20the%20remarks%20made%20by%20the%20different%20parties%2C%20the%20%E2%80%9CEU%E2%80%99s%20policy%20concerning%20Ukraine%20%5Bwill%5D%20not%20change%20%5Band%5D%20the%20EU%E2%80%99s%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20remains%20firm.%E2%80%9D%20Stano%20added%20that%20all%2027%20EU%20nations%20have%20agreed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfully%20support%20Ukraine%2C%E2%80%9D%20whilst%20ensuring%20that%20Kyiv%20can%20%E2%80%9Creinstate%20its%20territorial%20integrity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwhy-is-poland-no-longer-sending-arms-to-ukraine%2Fa-66889180%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Ftop-stories%2Fs-9097%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flogs1279.xiti.com%2Fhit.xiti%3Fs%3D531599%26s2%3D2%26p%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%3A%3Athewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26di%3D%26an%3D%26ac%3D%26x1%3D1%26x2%3D2%26x5%3Dthewire.in_Volltexte_JS%26x6%3D1%26x8%3Den-VAS-Volltexte-JavaScript-thewire.in-dwde%26x10%3Dthewire.in%3A%3AVolltexte%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695384926000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F20120344%2FAnti-terrorist_operation_in_eastern_Ukraine_War_Ukraine_26894689722.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhy-is-poland-no-longer-sending-arms-to-ukraine%22%2C%22summar