80%99t%20think%20this%20is%20possible%20for%20me%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sight%20of%20his%20dejected%20friend%20was%20unbearable%20to%20the%20Major.%20So%20he%20promised%20the%20lieutenant%20that%20he%20would%20make%20it%20happen%20for%20him.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20made%20a%20resolution%20in%20my%20heart%20to%20help%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20became%20the%20turning%20point%20of%20the%20Major%E2%80%99s%20life%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20work%20in%20this%20direction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20he%20voluntarily%20took%20an%20early%20retirement%20with%20a%20purpose%20in%20hand.%20The%20organisation%20CLAW%20Global%20was%20founded%20in%202019%20and%20has%20trained%20200%20people%20with%20disabilities%20in%20different%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F282597%2Fwoman-escapes-abusive-marriage-starts-adventure-sports-company-green-trek-assam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20adventure%20sports.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCLAW%20Global%20is%20not%20just%20an%20organisation%20that%20trains%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%20but%20it%20also%20tries%20to%20reinstill%20hope%20among%20them.%20I%20could%20see%20the%20positive%20energy%20they%20had%20and%20wanted%20to%20harness%20it%20in%20the%20right%20direction%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Finding%20ability%20in%20disabilities%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20with%20a%20core%20team%20of%20six%20members%20along%20with%2010%20other%20members%2C%20the%20organisation%20trains%20individuals%20with%20disabilities%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20paralysis%2C%20terminal%20diseases%2C%20visual%20impairments%2C%20and%20amputees%20%E2%80%94%20in%20adventure%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20on%20the%20time%20when%20he%20started%20brainstorming%20the%20idea%2C%20the%20Major%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20my%20research%2C%20I%20had%20one%20and%20only%20one%20goal%20in%20mind%20%E2%80%94%20take%20my%20friend%20scuba%20diving.%20So%20naturally%2C%20I%20started%20looking%20into%20the%20kind%20of%20resources%20required%20for%20a%20person%20with%20a%20disability%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CLAW%20Global%20has%20trained%20over%20200%20people%20in%20different%20types%20of%20adventure%20sports.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2Fclaw-1-1695382576-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-330672%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECLAW%20Global%20has%20trained%20over%20200%20people%20in%20different%20types%20of%20adventure%20sports.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Claw%20Global%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20out%20that%20the%20cost%20to%20acquire%20the%20resources%20and%20training%20was%20much%20more%20expensive%20than%20anticipated.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20making%20this%20available%20for%20one%20person%20would%20be%20expensive%20and%20that%20there%20must%20be%20many%20out%20there%20who%20want%20to%20do%20the%20same%20thing.%20This%20is%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20it%20on%20a