erly%20Twitter)%20enhanced%20suspense%3A%20%E2%80%9CAmid%20Amrit%20Kaal%20looking%20forward%20to%20have%20fruitful%20discussions%20and%20debate%20in%20Parliament.%E2%80%9D%20Most%20concluded%20that%20probably%20Joshi%2C%20too%2C%20was%20unaware%20of%20what%20was%20to%20be%20%E2%80%98discussed%20and%20debated%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECredence%20to%20this%20was%20added%20when%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20session%2C%20another%20minister%2C%20Prahlad%20Patel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpolicy%2Fwomen-reservation-bill-cleared-in-key-union-cabinet-meet-11695056861591.html%5C%22%3Edeleted%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20tweet%20stating%20that%20the%20Cabinet%20had%20cleared%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservations%20Bill%20and%20congratulated%20Modi%20for%20this.%20Many%20even%20concluded%20that%20probably%20Modi%2C%20too%2C%20was%20making%20up%20his%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20anxiety%20of%20people%20over%20what%20he%20was%20planning%20was%20typically%20a%20%E2%80%98Modisque%E2%80%99%20act%3A%20Occupy%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20mind%20space%20and%20force%20them%20to%20discuss%20him%20and%20his%20plans%20without%20knowing%20what%20they%20were.%20Modi%20likes%20nothing%20better%20than%20being%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20universe%20is%20a%20truism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20it%20transpired%20that%20even%20the%20majority%20within%20the%20BJP%20and%20perhaps%20even%20the%20council%20of%20ministers%20were%20clueless%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20the%20final%20call%20was%20yet%20to%20be%20taken.%20In%20all%20probability%2C%20options%20were%20weighed%20in%20for%20several%20days%20between%20the%20Session%20being%20convened%20and%20its%20actual%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20provided%20an%20indication%20of%20the%20growing%20assessment%20within%20the%20regime%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20and%20the%20parroting%20of%20so-called%20welfarism%20would%20not%20suffice.%20The%20two%20prongs%20require%20bolstering%20but%20not%20just%20by%20the%20time-tested%20Hindutva%20chorus%2C%20although%20efforts%20were%20made%20for%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20two%20forgotten%20rabbits%20were%20pulled%20out%20from%20the%20hat%3A%20The%20first%20being%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Quota%20Bill%2C%20which%20had%20remained%20confined%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%202014%20and%202019%20manifestos%20for%20the%20past%20nine%20years.%20After%20its%20passage%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20now%20going%20around%20showcasing%20it%20as%20a%20major%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20a%20hollow%20claim%20as%20actual%20reservations%20for%20women%20remain%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwomen-reservation-implementation-article-81-82-census-delimitation%5C%22%3Edistanced%20half-possibility%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20opposition%2C%20especially%20the%20INDIA%20parties%2C%20have%20smartly%20backed%20the%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26191526%2F1280px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26191526%2F1280px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26191526%2F1280px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi-300x146.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26191526%2F1280px-View_of_Lok_Sabha_chamber_in_the_New_Parliament_building_New_Delhi-1024x498.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665309%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22584%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGlimpses%20of%20the%20new%20Parliament%20Building%2C%20in%20New%20Delhi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20issue%20was%20another%20that%20was%20patronised%20for%20long%20by%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20simultaneous%20polls.%20A%20day%20after%20the%20Special%20Session%20was%20convened%2C%20the%20government%20let%20it%20be%20known%20that%20a%20committee%20was%20being%20established%20to%20recommend%20ways%20to%20transit%20to%20simultaneous%20polls%2C%20rhetorically%20called%20%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Poll%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fone-nation-one-election-one-leader-one-faith-one-business-house%5C%22%3EOne%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%2C%20One%20Leader%2C%20One%20Faith%2C%20One%20Business%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20too%20had%20been%20last%20heard%20of%20in%20June%202019%20at%20an%20all-party%20meeting.%20Thereafter%2C%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20mention%20till%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Special%20Session%20was%20convened.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20details%20triggered%20speculations%20%E2%80%93%20would%20the%20government%20attempt%20to%20bring%20Bills%20whose%20passage%20will%20ensure%20simultaneous%20polls%20along%20with%20the%20parliamentary%20poll%20due%20in%202024%3F%20For%20a%20day%20and%20a%20half%20there%20was%20no%20further%20information%20on%20its%20composition%20and%20terms%20of%20reference%20save%20that%20former%20President%20Ram%20Nath%20Kovind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-nation-one-election-fourth-committee%5C%22%3Ewould%20head%20it%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20emerged%20later%20that%20moves%20were%20afoot%20since%20June.%20But%2C%20like%20most%20crucial%20matters%2C%20total%20secrecy%20was%20the%20mantra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20chaotic%20act%20of%20a%20worried%20leadership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20plus%20two%20is%20not%20always%20four.%20On%20occasions%20when%20assessing%20moves%20of%20secretive%20regimes%2C%20the%20twos%20are%20often%20read%20as%20twenty-two.%20Conclusions%20were%20swiftly%20drawn.%20Discussions%20on%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20Special%20Session%20swung%20from%20one%20probability%20to%20another%2C%20from%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20to%20the%20legislative%20package%20for%20One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Poll%20and%20so%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20the%20government%20came%20out%20with%20a%20%E2%80%98tentative%E2%80%99%20agenda.%20It%20included%20neither%20issue%20on%20which%20there%20were%20speculations.%20The%20list%2C%20however%2C%20included%20the%20law%20that%20would%20further%20weaken%20the%20hollowed-out%20Election%20Commission%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Bill%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commissioners-appointment-bill-farewell-to-free-and-fair-elections%5C%22%3Eregulate%20the%20appointment%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20and%20the%20election%20commissioners%2C%20for%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20this%20was%20eventually%20not%20brought%20during%20the%20Special%20Session%20which%20was%20also%20shortened%20by%20a%20day.%20This%20only%20proves%20that%20there%20was%20little%20planning%20into%20convening%20it%2C%20but%20was%20just%20a%20chaotic%20act%20of%20a%20worried%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20for%20the%20Special%20Session%2C%20it%20may%20be%20recalled%2C%20was%20issued%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20weekend%20when%20opposition%20leaders%20were%20gathering%20in%20Mumbai%20for%20the%20third%20meeting%20of%20what%20had%20by%20then%20acquired%20the%20acronym%20of%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMedia%20organisations%20had%20drawn%20plans%20to%20report%20and%20comment%20on%20the%20developments%2C%20outcomes%2C%20and%20emerging%20political%20drift.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwomens-reservation-modi-government-hurry-propose-not-wed%5C%22%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%3A%20Modi%20Government%20in%20Tearing%20Hurry%20to%20Propose%20but%20Not%20to%20Wed%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20plans%20were%20forcibly%20altered%2C%20if%20not%20shelved.%20Eventually%2C%20multiple%20objectives%20were%20met%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Mumbai%20meet%20did%20not%20receive%20the%20kind%20of%20coverage%20it%20would%20have%20otherwise%20got.%20Modi%20and%20his%20intended%20moves%20were%20the%20only%20issues%20that%20got%20written%20about%20and%20discussed%2C%20on%20TV%20and%20among%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20second%20time%20after%20the%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20Bengaluru%20meeting%20that%20team%20Modi%20scheduled%20another%20%E2%80%98event%E2%80%99%3B%20in%20that%20case%20a%20resurrection%20of%20the%20NDA%20which%20met%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20the%202019%20verdict.%20There%20was%20a%20third%20occasion%20too%20%E2%80%93%20when%20the%20first%20INDIA%20coordination%20panel%20was%20virtually%20blanked%20out%20by%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20the%20BJP%20office%20to%20receive%20accolades%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98successful%E2%80%99%20hosting%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20forced%20to%20revive%20its%20alliance%20because%20now%20the%20bigger%20party%20%E2%80%98requires%E2%80%99%20the%20smaller%20ones%2C%20not%20the%20other%20way%20around%20as%20Modi%20theorised%20once%20while%20stating%20that%20parties%20struck%20alliances%20with%20the%20bigger%20parties%20to%20improve%20%E2%80%98winnability%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWeeks%20before%2C%20violence%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-violence-rpf-constables-murder-new-phase-anti-muslim-hate%5C%22%3Ehad%20erupted%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Nuh%2C%20a%20district%20in%20the%20BJP-governed%20Haryana%2C%20and%20people%20had%20lined%20up%20against%20one%20another%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religious%20identity%2C%20adding%20to%20similar%20happenings%20since%20May%2C%20courtesy%20of%20the%20Manipur%20mayhem.%20Another%20round%20of%20provocation%20in%20Nuh%20was%20quelled%20in%20August-end%2C%20demonstrating%20riots%20occur%20only%20when%20the%20government%20does%20not%20act%20to%20prevent%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDays%20before%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20another%20distraction%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20discourse%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwatch-what-strategic-purpose-is-served-by-changing-our-countrys-name-to-bharat-vivek-katju%5C%22%3EBharat%20becoming%20the%20preferred%20country%20name%3C%2Fa%3E.%20More%20grist%20to%20the%20gossip%20mills%20%E2%80%93%20as%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%E2%80%99s%20dinner%20invitation%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20tour%20itinerary%20for%20the%2020th%20ASEAN-India%20Summit%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Bharat%2C%20and%20finally%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fg20-summit%2Fstory%2Fg20-summit-bharat-name-displayed-in-front-of-pm-modi-during-inaugural-address-397587-2023-09-09%5C%22%3Enameplate%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20front%20of%20him%20during%20the%20New%20Delhi%20Summit%20%E2%80%93%20seen%20by%20many%20as%20portent%20of%20formal%20alteration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22165508%2FH20230909138364.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22165508%2FH20230909138364.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22165508%2FH20230909138364-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22165508%2FH20230909138364-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F22165508%2FH20230909138364-800x400.jpg%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-674376%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20nameplate%20before%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20said%20%E2%80%98Bharat%E2%80%99.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20turned%20down%20a%20requisition%20to%20rename%20India%20as%20Bharat%20in%202014-15%20when%20petitioned%20by%20an%20individual.%20It%20did%20not%20alter%20its%20stance%20even%20when%20the%20matter%20went%20up%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20smart%20nomenclature%20has%20disturbed%20Modi.%20The%20alliance%20has%20to%20be%20dissed%2C%20but%20how%20can%20he%20refer%20to%20the%20alliance%20as%20INDIA%3F%20As%20a%20result%2C%20two%20words%20were%20added%20to%20the%20political%20vocabulary%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fname-of-our-alliance-has-got-under-their-skin-shashi-tharoors-counter-to-bjp-over-ghamandia-remark%2Farticleshow%2F103711155.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3EINDI%20Alliance%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fit-is-ghamandia-gatbhandan-pm-modi-attacks-oppositions-india%2Farticleshow%2F102613216.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eghamandia%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Bard%20was%20obviously%20wrong%20%E2%80%93%20names%20are%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESomewhere%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20these%20fresh%20openings%2C%20the%20BJP-Modi%20combine%20was%20handed%20another%20playing%20card%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhat-is-sanatana-dharma%5C%22%3ESanatan%20Dharma%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Misquoting%20or%20distorting%20words%20of%20the%20tallest%20of%20nationalist%20icons%20%E2%80%93%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Bal%20G