a%20called%20Shalukar%20Bol.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20idol%20was%20unique%20as%20it%20depicted%20the%20deity%20killing%20a%20demon.%20Made%20of%20wood%20and%20bran%2C%20the%20imagery%20was%20far%20from%20the%20usual%20calm%20and%20composed%20demeanour%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261867%2Fhow-to-carve-clay-ganesh-idol-chathurthi-sustainable-hack-eco-friendly%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eof%20Lord%20Ganesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20this%20was%20symbolic%20of%20India%20as%20a%20nation%20fighting%20for%20its%20freedom%20against%20the%20colonialists.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20gained%20more%20attention%20when%20freedom%20fighter%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20praised%20his%20efforts%20in%20an%20article%20in%20the%20iconic%20newspaper%20%3Cem%3EKesari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Over%20a%20century%20later%2C%20the%20original%20idol%20made%20of%20paper%20pulp%20is%20still%20worshipped%20at%20Bhausaheb%20Rangari%E2%80%99s%20wada.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDid%20you%20find%20the%20story%20interesting%3F%20Watch%20this%20short%20video%20to%20find%20out%20more%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%20%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAu35GJHjHWE%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranit